des:
Nuthin’ but the best in late 40's and 50's Blues, RnR, Jive, Swing, Stroll, Early Soul,
Jump Blues, Western Swing plus Vocal Group R&B Doo Wop Rockers of the Big Beat.
It’s all about those who support the roots music of those decades
Plus all the DJ's who give their devoted time for all to enjoy what they play.
